profile:
Bergeron Drywall and Painting Co. was formed in April of 2018 by myself and my partner. I have over 15 years experience as a drywall taper and am also a very skilled drywall installer.
Bergeron Drywall and Painting Co. is also able to provide renovations such as interior framing and painting. We are very experienced in many types of interior renovations and always provide reliable professional service.
